v 3
d driveuse. Use datasets from Google Drive with cross-platform path handling
d
d driveuse is a wrapper for 'use' that automatically detects the local 
d path to Google Drive on both macOS and Windows. It creates global 
d shortcuts $driveuse and $sf for easy path construction.
d
d Author: Eric A. Booth, Sr Researcher, Texas2036.org
d Support: eric.a.booth@gmail.com
d
